<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:60.54px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">③</span><span class="cls_005"> </span><span class="cls_008">山田さんは</span><span class="cls_005">   </span><span class="cls_008">事務所です。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:370.80px;top:62.40px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">山田先生在辦公室。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.80px;top:80.94px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">３ </span><span class="cls_002">.    </span><span class="cls_008">どこ</span><span class="cls_005">／</span><span class="cls_008">どちら</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:101.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">「</span><span class="cls_008">どこ</span><span class="cls_009">」「</span><span class="cls_008">どちら</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:159.00px;top:101.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">」是分別表示場所和方向的疑問詞。詢問場所時也可以用「</span><span class="cls_008">ど</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:121.80px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">ちら</span></div>
