<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:142.14px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">④</span><span class="cls_005"> </span><span class="cls_008">お手洗いは</span><span class="cls_002">  </span><span class="cls_008">どこですか。</span></div>
