<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:223.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">此外</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">在詢問國家、公司、學校等所屬的場所和組織名時</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">疑問詞應是「</span><span class="cls_008">どこ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:502.20px;top:223.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">」</span></div>
