<div style="position:absolute;left:409.80px;top:244.14px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">」更鄭重。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:89.40px;top:260.94px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">がっ こう</span></div>
