<div style="position:absolute;left:324.00px;top:366.60px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">の</span><span class="cls_009">」是指該公司生產的。這個疑</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:53.40px;top:386.94px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">問句中的疑問詞用「</span><span class="cls_008">どこ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:198.60px;top:386.94px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">」。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:407.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">⑧</span><span class="cls_005"> </span><span class="cls_008">これは</span><span class="cls_002">  </span><span class="cls_008">どこの</span><span class="cls_002">  </span><span class="cls_008">コンピューターですか。</span></div>
